{"tid":2309311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【我係五毛？】入黎話你知連登仔咁憎袁國勇既四大原因！！！！","createTime":"2020-12-02T12:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T13:15:19.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"627aa55c91e841588aa605c98004ac3572cdf822","tid":2309311,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"格黎PO有人問點解咁憎袁國勇<br />\n認為＂客觀D講佢其實由頭到尾都只係做緊醫生責任＂<br />\n<br />\n點解大家咁憎袁國勇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308769\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308769</a><br />\n<br />\n咁講返香港政府<br />\n林鄭都<strong>＂由頭到尾都只係做緊特首責任＂</strong>防疫<br />\n林鄭都只係係蒙面法仍然生效既同時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推出左強制口罩令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又推出港安碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>又推出強制檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n點解你地又會咁大反應?<br />\n我又係咪可以話你地自己以小心之心度君子之腹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">咁講下袁生最撐既強制檢測</span></span></strong><br />\n強制檢測完全violate病人私隱同埋病人權益<br />\n醫院啲病人約章係咪變哂垃圾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkapo.org.hk/病人權益/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkapo.org.hk%2F%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=fef68fa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkapo.org.hk/病人權益/</a><br />\n病人的權利，包括五方面：<br />\n醫治權<br />\n知悉權<br />\n決定權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私隱權<br />\n申訴權<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>決定權</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">１有權接受或拒絕任何藥物、檢驗或療法，並獲知所作決定可能引起的後果</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁不如講下袁生做左乜野?<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">1. 袁國勇：支持強制檢測，如果不驗便找警察、衞生署職員，如果都不肯要罰款或監禁</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2241076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2241076</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViJPNG9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViJPNG9.png&h=7c647f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">2. 繼續幫強制檢測護航</span></strong><br />\n袁國勇：強制檢測不是侵犯人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2293082\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2293082</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">３. 怪責市民，令市民產生罪感自然唔再挑戰政府既防疫政策，簡單黎講又係權威式管治<br />\n袁國勇指港第四波疫情純粹香港市民的錯</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308724\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308724</a><br />\n<br />\n４.<span class=\"xx-large\"> <strong><span class=\"red\">身為中國工程院院士，國家衛健委高級別專家組成員，香港政府防疫專家顧問團成員</span></strong></span>，最撚叻就扮中立持平，信任呢Ｄ野有時都係信個人，你信左呢條友，第日政府用呢條友個口講任何暴政，市民就會容易受好多<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">結論:連登仔精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n慢慢繼續做恐懼撚endorse政府既防疫政策<br />\n成班傻鳩自願放棄自己權益同埋人身自由，仲要覺得唔錯，真係好撚ＯＮ９<br />\n<br />\n延申閱讀<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">1: 上年流感死既人真係多過今年武肺</span></strong><br />\nTrump又中，其實武肺just a flu<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2306237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2306237</a>"},{"pid":"6db1ff8ae2e6572b03180e4ea17d7533d5a38b93","tid":2309311,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a81f2729ac82c27e65c4b67d407c0b8532780ee","tid":2309311,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"